      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "明日は早めに出ないとですね。リハにはうちの橋本が\n立ち合います。こちらは任せて下さい。それでは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1678197589,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4406.806062899999,
          "startTime": 10.5746258218
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.5746258218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？　お兄ちゃんと\n何話してたんですか？　随分仲良さそうでしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.503340207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.292137647
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、明日の出演のことを……って、す、すみれ！？\nあ、兄同士でちょっと情報交換をしてたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.157139305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.3162131745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん同士で……！？\n私がいない間にですか！？　ず、ずるい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4162131626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、普通だよ？　……そういえば、一週間口利かない\nって言っていたけど、普通に話してるそうじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.545503255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.1920409638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれは勢いで言っただけで……\nって、お兄ちゃんとそんなこと話してたんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2587076186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "他に何を話し合ったんですか。正直に言って下さい\n恥ずか……誤解を招く話があったらいけませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7253742853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.1587076305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "他？　そ、そうだなぁ……お兄さんからは\nすみれが家の手伝いを頑張っている、って聞いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんが……そっか\n私のこと、そんな風に話してくれてたなら嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2210207938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.3876874724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんと{user}さんが仲良くなって\n私だけ仲間外れになったら……って不安になっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7221650406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "仲間外れなんて……そんなことある訳ないだろ\n俺がご家族と話すのは、全部すみれのことなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.6416782814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですよね……。家族がみんな授業参観に\n来られないからって、気にしちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0083449362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1083449481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、東京のお兄ちゃんが来てくれるからもう平気です\nなんだか楽しみで、今日は眠れないかもしれません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1750116029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3083449481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ご両親に挨拶した時、場所と時間も聞いたしな\n明日は遅れないように中学校に向かうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれも、明日は移動もライブの収録もあるんだし\n今日はなるべくゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9650528245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.5383909342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、ちゃんと休めるように頑張りまーす！\n……自信はないですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.205057589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――授業参観当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2050576009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4717283246
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4717283246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、来てくれたんですね！\n嬉しいっちゃ～！　……あっ、つい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5383909223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はは、山形弁が出る程喜んでくれてるんだな\nしっかり見て、ご両親にも様子を伝えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6008411906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.2475600994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、お願いします！\n後でお父さん達に私の活躍をしっかり伝えて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.5142226852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.0475600994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は楽しみ過ぎて、全然眠れなくて……\n気付いたら朝になってたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.6808893518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "授業の予習とか、これまでの復習とか……\n一つ気になったら、もう止まらなくなっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3475682255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.6809158123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か？　まったく、昨日休むように言ったのに……\n休み時間に少しでも休めたらいいんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、大丈夫ですよ。今は全然眠くないんです！\nむしろ冴えちゃってるくらいですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.7946307496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.2946348305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ授業が始まる時間ですね\nしっかり頑張るので、見ていて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8612974163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.7946307496
